rows.label: tlk43600143_02_msg0001
rows.name:
So you know how I was complaining
about the cost of living going up?

rows.label: tlk43600143_02_msg0004
rows.name:
From what my son tells me, the price
of commodities should drop as Invidia
develops as a country.

rows.label: tlk43600143_02_msg0005
rows.name:
The more we buy and sell, and the
more problems we solve, the more
we'll improve.

rows.label: tlk43600143_02_msg0006
rows.name:
There's little I can do to contribute
at my age, but you youngsters can
certainly do something to help.
